data.description: Own a piece of history!! Antique Colonial Farmhouse formerly known as the Wayside Inn is waiting for you and your creative ideas to bring this home back to life! Upon entering the huge Family Room with Stone Fireplace formerly known as the carriage house will be the place for family gatherings; relaxing by the fire or curling up w/a book. The home features a large dining room perfect for enjoying meals w/family & friends. Off the Dining Rm is an ideal office/den space and front to back Living Rm w/wood flooring. 1 st flr lav & laundry are handy.  The 2nd flr offers plenty of room with a Lrg Main Bedroom w/walk in closet. 2 full baths & plenty of space for bedrooms/teen suite/ office/ craft room. One bedroom also features access to a nice size deck. The large attic offers the opportunity for even more living space. There is a nice size deck for enjoying your morning coffee, relaxing at the end of the day, bbq's and outdoor dining. Imagine the future potential here!
